    "description": {
      "content": "The data API provides programmatic access to BEA published economic statistics using industry-standard methods and procedures. BEA's data API includes methods for retrieving a subset of our statistical data and the meta-data that describes it. The data API and its documentation are for programmers who are familiar with the concepts and techniques of retrieving data from Web Services.",
